Daga Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020, yawan adadin cututtukan coronavirus (COVID-19) ya karu cikin sauri a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai.
Yawan adadin cututtukan cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, wanda ke nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 ta duniya tana yaduwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe duk da cewa tana da matakai daban-daban a kowace ƙasa.
Bisa ga kwarewar Italiya, ƙasashe, asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani suna buƙatar haɓaka shirye -shiryen su don tsammanin ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu rahoton wasu mutane da ke fama da cutar sankarar bargo a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 9 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da rahoton cewa sabon kwayar cutar coronavirus ne ke haifar da cutar, wanda ake kira mai tsanani na numfashi coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Shaidar da aka samu ya nuna cewa kusan kashi 80% na marasa lafiya da ke da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato, kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi tare da cutar huhu ko a waje da cutar huhu, kuma yawancin suna murmurewa.
A cikin kashi 14% na masu cutar kansa, COVID-19 yana ci gaba zuwa wani mataki mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6% ke fuskantar rashin lafiya mai tsanani wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Kashi 4% na marasa lafiya da ke asibiti da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 sun mutu.
A cikin wannan binciken, muna kimanta yanayin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila (UK) kuma muna kwatanta shi da lardin Hubei na China.
A halin yanzu, mun kwatanta adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya da adadin masu cutar a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa daga China zuwa wasu yankuna na ƙasa, kuma annobar COVID-19 a halin yanzu tana nunawa a duniya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Spiteri et al. a cikin Eurosurveillance 2020, wanda aka buga a ranar 5 ga Maris, sun ba da rahoton farkon shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka tabbatar a Turai bisa ga fassarar WHO.
A cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai, Faransa ce ta ba da rahoton mutane uku da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020, waɗanda suka fito daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an sami shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashe 30 na Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Ingila, tare da 39,768 shari'o'i da mutuwar 1,727 a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2020, daga cikinsu akwai 17,750 shari'o'i da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kawai.
Sanin yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan abin da ke faruwa
Bayanai game da lambobin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya kamar yadda aka ruwaito a Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) sun fito ne kawai daga kafofin hukuma kamar su Ma'aikatar Kiwon Lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, wanda ake sabuntawa kowace safiya da ƙarfe 8:00.
An yi amfani da waɗannan bayanan don kimanta abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin COVID-19 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya da kwatanta su da Italiya.
Ganin cewa kasancewar masu cutar COVID-19 masu aiki wakili ne, mun kimanta yawan adadin COVID-19 na kwanaki 14, kuma a sakamakon haka, mun yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya daga Janairu 1 zuwa Maris 15, 2020.
Bugu da ƙari, mun kwatanta adadin masu cutar a kowace ƙasa har zuwa karfe 8:00 na safe na ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da adadin waɗanda aka ruwaito a Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Yanayin da aka nuna a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya na shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 na lokacin ya biyo bayan lardin Hubei (China) gaba ɗaya (Hoto 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya, yawan adadin COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu/2020 (Mataki na gaba).
Wannan ya fi yawaita ne saboda saurin karuwar shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma, sauran ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan yanayin karuwa a cikin adadin COVID-19 (Kayan taimako).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU / EU Economic Area da United Kingdom idan aka kwatanta da adadin a Italiya daga Janairu 31-Maris 15, 2020.
Har zuwa karfe 8:00 na safiyar ranar 15 ga Maris, wasu ƙasashe 15 na Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton jimlar adadin masu cutar kamar Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da aka ruwaito sun karu cikin sauri a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya.
Yanayin da ake samu a cikin yanayin COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar ta duniya tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a kusan kowace ƙasa.
Wannan yana faruwa yayin da ƙasashe ke cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance a cikin amsoshin lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa, kuma wataƙila ma'anar shari'ar daban-daban da ladabi daban-daban a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da kasancewar COVID-19.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a lardunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana cewa kusan kashi 10% na marasa lafiyar COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ba da rahoton cewa asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan lardunan sun cika.
A halin yanzu, EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai yana da bayanai game da adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da ke asibiti da / ko kula da kulawa mai tsanani don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanan ba).
Duk da haka, dole ne a tattara su ta hanyar da ta dace don ƙarfafa bayanan sa ido na yau da kullun, wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin rahotanni da mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka yi a shekara ta 2010/11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin gadajen kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, daga gado 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a Portugal ga kowane mutum 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun wadata fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje masu kulawa da matsakaici da matsakaici ga kowane mutum 100,000, a 201011).
Ana ba da ƙididdigar yawan adadin masu cutar COVID da aka gano a cikin dakunan kwanan dalibai a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya, a cikin sabuntawar ECDC ta shida, a cikin kimantawar COVID-19 mai sauri.
Saboda akwai wasu lokuta a cikin ƙasashen EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, kuma asibitoci da dakunan kulawa da hankali galibi suna ba da sabis ga wasu ɓangarorin al'umma, ana buƙatar bayyana bayanai game da lokuta da gadajen kulawa da hankali a matakin Statistics 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da sauran abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 ta duniya tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya.
