Kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin wani sabon kimantawa na haɗari na ECDC, yana da mahimmanci a ɗauki hanzari da cikakkiyar hanyar rage yaduwar SARS-COV-2, maimakon rage cutar zuwa ragewa, saboda karuwar saurin da ake tsammani a cikin adadin masu cutar idan ba a aiwatar da shi ba da daɗewa ba ba zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaitawa da amsar su ba.
