A watan Disamba na 2019, sabon coronavirus (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da barkewar cutar, wanda yanzu ake kira cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sake sanya wa kwayar cutar suna mai tsanani na cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annobar duniya.
Don yaƙar cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta shirya jagorar shawarwari na gaggawa kuma an buga ta akan layi a cikin binciken likita na soja a ranar 06 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Tun da aka buga shi, an mai da hankali sosai ga wannan littafin.
Ka tuna, kodayake, cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, fahimtarmu da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali bisa ga binciken da ake samu yanzu da kuma ayyukan asibiti; saboda haka hanyoyin bincike da hanyoyin magani suna ci gaba da ingantawa.
Misali, Jagororin Ganowa da Kula da Lafiya na COVID-19 da Kwamitin Kiwon Lafiya na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) ya bayar, wanda ya fito a cikin jimlar fitowa bakwai daga ranar 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, tare da wasu canje-canje masu mahimmanci.
Yanzu jagorarmu ta karɓi ra'ayoyi daga gare su, waɗanda suka ba da shawarar sauƙaƙe sakamakon sakamakon bisa ga kwarewar asibiti.
Aikin su ya kawo mana sabon shaida da kuma amfani ga cutar a duk duniya.
Muna goyon bayan wannan aiki mai muhimmanci kuma muna godiya.
