Binciken tabbataccen yanayin ya kamata ya dogara ne akan yanayin da ake zargi: (1) tabbataccen gwajin PCR na ainihin lokacin SARS-CoV-2; (2) cikakken tsarin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar wanda ke nuna rashin jituwa ga sanannen sabon coronavirus; (3) gwajin ƙwayar cuta don takamaiman IgM antigen da IgG antigen don SARS-CoV-2 mai kyau a cikin gwajin kunne, ko canji daga mara kyau zuwa tabbatacce daga takamaiman IgG antigen zuwa SARS-CoV-2, ko sau 4 a matakin murmurewa fiye da lokaci mai tsanani.
Ana iya ganin gwajin PCR na ainihi don kwayar nucleic acid a cikin numfashi ko samfuran jini don ƙarin bugu na biyu (Janairu 182020) da na uku (Janairu 222020).
An ƙara gwajin gwajin jini a fitowar ta huɗu (Janairu 272020) da ta biyar (Fabrairu 82020).
Waɗannan gyare-gyare, waɗanda suka dogara da aikin da masu binciken ke ci gaba da yi, za su taimaka wajan gano ingantattun kayan aikin nucleic acid don saurin bincike da kuma ƙara samfuran numfashi daban-daban, gami da samfurin jini, da kuma samar da sakamako mai kyau na ƙwayoyin cuta na musamman a cikin ma'aunin da aka tabbatar.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin bayanai da ke nuna cewa ya kamata mu mai da hankali ga marasa lafiya da ke da alamun cutar da kuma waɗanda ba su da alamun cutar.
Saboda haka, saboda an rarrabe mutane ba tare da alamun asibiti a matsayin masu haɗari ba, ana buƙatar sake fasalin jadawalin aikin Zhou et al.
