Muna ba da shawarar yin bincike game da shari'ar da ba a zata ba da kuma zargin da ba a tabbatar ba, bin sabbin umarnin ƙasashen da suka fito.
Ƙungiyarmu tana ci gaba da ɗaukaka ƙa'idodinmu don taimaka wa mutane.
Bangladesh ta ba da rahoton sabbin mutuwar biyar mafi girma a rana saboda COVID-19
A jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da sabbin mutuwar biyar a ranar sakamakon COVID-19.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutane da suka mutu a rana guda sakamakon cutar.
Har zuwa jiya, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Bincike ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton asarar da cutar ta yi, wanda ya haɗa da mutane 114 da ke jinya da kuma 33 da suka warke.
An samu mutuwar mutane 17 a cikin jimlar.
A cikin wani rahoto na labarai a yanar gizo, Daraktan IEDCR, Dokta Mirjaddi Sabrina Flora, ya ce cikin wadanda suka mutu akwai maza hudu da mace daya.
A cewar Dr. Merjaday, marasa lafiya biyu sun haura shekaru 60, biyu suna tsakanin shekaru 51 zuwa 60, daya kuma yana tsakanin shekaru 41 zuwa 50.
