Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba ta duniya
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana yaduwar COVID-19 a matsayin annobar duniya da cutar coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa.
Kalmar "Pan-Am" ba ta nuna irin yanayin da cutar ke da shi ba, amma kawai yadda ta yadu, kuma hakan ya nuna cewa gwamnatocin WHO sun dauki mataki cikin gaggawa:
"Duk ƙasashe har yanzu suna iya canza yanayin annobar".
"Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus ya ce, "" idan ƙasashe suka bincika, su kula, su ware, su bincika, kuma su ba da amsa ga jama'a, """
"A cikin wannan yanayin, muna bukatar mu yi aiki tuƙuru don mu magance matsalar.
"A cewar tsohon darektan kula da rigakafin cututtuka na Amurka, Dokta Tom Frieden, cutar ta zama ""ba a taɓa gani ba""".
"A cikin wata sanarwa da aka buga a CNN a watan Fabrairu, ya ce, ""Babu wani kwayar cuta ta numfashi da ta faru banda mura tun daga lokacin da ta faru har zuwa lokacin da ta sake yaduwa a duniya"."
"Gera Jesus ya bayyana ra'ayi iri ɗaya cewa ba mu ga annoba kamar coronavirus ba. """
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "kuma ba mu taɓa ganin annobar da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci guda ba".
Wannan sabon yanayin ya biyo bayan shawarar da Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta yanke na ayyana yaduwar cutar a matsayin gaggawa ga lafiyar jama'a.
Darakta na Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Kasa ta Amurka, Dr. Anthony Fusey, ya ce cutar ta kara tsanantawa saboda yaduwar cutar ta shiga cikin al'umma.
Tun daga ranar Alhamis, Associated Press ta ba da rahoton cewa akwai mutane 126,000 da ke da cutar COVID-19 a duk duniya, kuma fiye da 4,600 sun mutu sakamakon hakan.
Cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ta 2019 20 annobar cutar kwayar cutar coronavirus ce ta 2019 (COVID-19) wacce ke ci gaba da yaduwa, kuma tana haifar da cutar coronavirus mai saurin kamuwa da cuta ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
An ayyana cutar a matsayin gaggawa ta duniya ga lafiyar jama'a a Wuhan, China, Disamba 2019, Janairu 30th, 2020; an ayyana cutar a ranar 11th, 2020 Maris.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, an samu kusan mutane miliyan 1.61 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 a kasashe 210, wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 97,000.
An warkar da mutane kusan 364,000.
An kiyasta cewa adadin mutuwar cutar ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari a China, kuma a sauran sassan duniya, ya kai kashi 13.04 cikin dari a Algeria zuwa .08 cikin dari a New Zealand.
Alamun alamun sune zazzabi, tari, da wahalar numfashi.
Matsaloli sun haɗa da ciwon huhu da ciwon damuwa na gaggawa.
Lokaci daga lokacin kamuwa da cutar zuwa bayyanar alamun cutar yawanci kwanaki biyar ne, amma zai iya zama daga kwana biyu zuwa goma sha huɗu.
Babu wani allurar rigakafi ko magani da aka tsara don cutar.
Babban magani shine alamomi da tallafi. Matakan kariya da aka ba da shawarar sun haɗa da wanke hannu, rufe baki lokacin yin fitsari, nisantawa da wasu mutane, da lura da kai da keɓewa ga waɗanda suke tunanin sun kamu da cutar.
Hukumomi a duk duniya sun amsa ta hanyar aiwatar da takunkumin hana tafiye-tafiye, keɓewa, ƙuntatawa na lokaci, sarrafa haɗarin aiki, da rufe wuraren aiki.
Cutar ta haifar da mummunan damuwa na zamantakewar tattalin arziki a duniya, jinkiri da soke wasannin wasanni, abubuwan addini, siyasa da al'adu, da kuma ƙarancin kayayyaki a cikin tashin hankali.
Makarantun sakandare da jami'o'i a cikin ƙasashe 193 a cikin gida ko na duniya sun rufe, wanda ya shafi kusan kashi 99.4 na yawan ɗalibai.
