b'Angiotensin -converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne da ke cikin ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin huhu, jijiyoyin jini, zuciya, koda, da hanji.
ACE2 yana hana aikin enzyme mai canza angotensin (ACE) ta hanyar rage matakin angostatin-II da haɓaka Ang (1-7), yana mai da shi mai yiwuwa maƙasudin magunguna don magance cututtukan jijiyoyin jini. ACE2 yana aiki azaman hanyar shiga cikin sel don wasu coronavirus.
Ana kiran enzyme a cikin mutane hACE2.
Angostatin-enzyme 2 wani sinadarin zinc ne mai dauke da sinadarin iron wanda ake samu a cikin endothelial da sauran kwayoyin halitta.
Ana sanya furotin ACE2 zuwa yankin N-terminal peptidase M2 da yankin C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter.
ACE2 shine nau'in membrane na I wanda yake da cutarwa, kuma an samo shi a cikin huhu da sauran sassan jiki saboda enzyme yana da yanki mai aiki.
Wani enzyme mai suna Shadas ya yanke ɓangaren waje na ACE2 daga ɓangaren ƙwayoyin halitta, kuma sakamakon ya zama furotin mai narkewa wanda aka saki cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe ya fita cikin fitsari.
Ana samun ACE2 a yawancin gabobin jiki: ACE2 yana da alaƙa da enzymes na ƙwayoyin alveolar na nau'in II na huhu, ƙananan hanji, ƙwayoyin jini da jijiyoyin jini da ƙwayoyin tsoka mai laushi a yawancin gabobin jiki.
Ana bayyana mRNA na ACE2 a cikin ƙwayar kwakwalwa, stratum, hypothalamus da ƙwayoyin kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine daidaitawa na ACE.
ACE yana canza hormone angiotensin I zuwa angiotensin II mai ƙuntatawar jini.
ACE2 kuma yana yanke carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) a cikin farji kuma yana sarrafa shi zuwa hydrolyzed zuwa vasodilator angiotestin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya kawar da [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, da ghrelin, da sauran peptides da yawa.
ACE2 kuma yana sarrafa membrane na SLC6A19, mai jigilar amino acid mara tsaka tsaki, wanda aka sani yana da alaƙa da cutar Heartburn.
A matsayin furotin mai wucewa, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban wurin shiga ga wasu kwayoyin cutar coronavirus, gami da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (kwayar cutar da ke haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, sun haɗa sunadarai na S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 zuwa ƙwayoyin ƙwayoyin cuta na ACE2 kuma suna ba da damar kwayar cutar da enzymes zuwa cikin ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma kewayawa.
Wannan aikin shigarwa yana buƙatar samfoti na S-protein akan mai sarrafawa na TMPRSS2, wanda a halin yanzu shine magani da ake bincike. Wannan ya sa wasu suka yi tunanin cewa zai iya taimakawa wajen yaƙar kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar rage matakin ACE2 a cikin kwayar halitta.
Koyaya, ƙungiyoyi da yawa na ƙwararru da hukumomin kulawa suna ba da shawarar ci gaba da maganin ACE mai hanawa da ARB na yau da kullun.
A cikin wani bita da meta-bincike da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012, FDA ta gano cewa amfani da masu hana ACE yana da raguwar ciwon huhu na 34% idan aka kwatanta da sarrafawa.
Hakanan, haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu ya kasance daidai da marasa lafiya da aka kula da cutar ACE tare da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar huhu, musamman a cikin kwakwalwa da rashin ƙarfi na zuciya.
An kuma yi amfani da masu hana ACE don magance mutuwar da ke da alaƙa da ciwon huhu, kuma sakamakon ya kasance ƙasa da haɗarin ciwon huhu gaba ɗaya.
Kwayar halittar mutum ta ACE2 (rhACE2) ana tsammanin sabon magani ne don cutar huhu mai saurin tashi, wanda ke inganta haɓakar jini da iskar oxygen a cikin fararen alade da ke fama da cutar ta fatar jiki ta liposaccharide.
Rabin rayuwar rhACE2 a cikin ɗan adam kusan awanni 10 ne kuma farkon aikinsa yana da mintuna 30 ban da sa'o'i 24 na aiki (lokaci).
Yawancin binciken sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama kyakkyawan magani ga cututtukan da ke da ƙwayoyin cuta na renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors) ko kuma masu cutar angiotensin II. An kimanta rhACE2 mai shiga cikin gwaji don maganin cututtukan damuwa na numfashi mai tsanani.
Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na wayar hannu waɗanda aka tsara don taimakawa wajen bin diddigin ko gano hanyoyin gano mutane (lamba) waɗanda wataƙila sun haɗu da mutumin da ke da cutar.
A wasu sassan gwamnati da yankuna, an shirya ko kuma an gabatar da aikace-aikace da yawa tare da taimakon gwamnati.
An samar da tsarin da yawa don gina aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba.
Musamman, damuwa game da sirrin sirri ya taso game da tsarin da ke bin diddigin wurin masu amfani da aikace-aikacen.
Zaɓuɓɓukan ƙananan tsangwama sun haɗa da amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rajistar kusanci da mai amfani da sauran wayoyin hannu.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun sanar da cewa za su yi aiki tare don daidaita ayyukan na'urori masu amfani da Bluetooth zuwa tsarin aiki na Android da iOS.
A China, gwamnatin kasar Sin, tare da haɗin gwiwar Alipay, ta haɓaka aikace-aikacen wayar hannu wanda ke sanar da 'yan ƙasa idan sun tuntuɓi mutane da ke da COVID-19.
Ana amfani da shi a birane sama da 200 na kasar Sin. Ana amfani da wata manhaja mai suna TraceTogether a Singapore.
An samar da aikace-aikacen ta hanyar al'ummar IT ta yankin da aka saki a matsayin tushen budewa kuma an ba da shi ga gwamnati. A Arewacin Macedonia, Gwamnatin ta ƙaddamar da aikace-aikacen Bluetooth-based  StopKorona! don saka idanu kan haɗari da kuma amsawa da sauri ga waɗanda ke da cutar.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya ne suka samar da manhajar.
Tun daga ranar 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, aikace-aikacen yana jiran izini don zama a cikin Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
"A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta bayyana cewa aikace-aikacen neman lamba yana cikin babban ci gaba. Hakanan ana shirin yin irin wannan aikace-aikacen a Ireland da Faransa ("StopCovid") wanda zai fara aiki a cikin makonni".
Dukansu Ostiraliya da New Zealand suna la'akari da aikace-aikace dangane da aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha na shirin gabatar da aikace-aikacen geofencing don marasa lafiya na COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow don hana su barin gidajensu.
Ross Anderson, Farfesa a fannin Injiniyan Tsaro a Jami'ar Cambridge, ya lissafa matsaloli da yawa, gami da yiwuwar sakamako mara kyau na karya wanda zai iya amfani da shi ga tsarin aikace-aikacen da kuma idan amfani da aikace-aikacen ya iyakance ga ƙananan ɓangarorin jama'a.
"Domin magance damuwa game da yaduwar aikace-aikacen ɓatarwa ko cutarwa na ""coronavirus"", Apple ya sanya iyaka kan waɗanne nau'ikan kamfanoni za su iya ƙara aikace-aikacen da ke da alaƙa da cutar coronavirus zuwa Shagon App, yana iyakance su ga Zyphify ko manyan kamfanoni".
Google da Amazon sun sanya irin wannan ƙuntatawa.
Masu kare hakkin sirri sun nuna damuwa game da tasirin sa ido mai yawa ta amfani da aikace-aikacen coronavirus, musamman cewa kayan aikin leken asiri da aka kirkira don magance cutar coronavirus na duniya za su rushe da zarar barazanar ta wuce.
Amnesty International da wasu kungiyoyi sama da 100 sun yi kira da a kawo karshen irin wannan leken asiri.
