Koyaya, ba duk tsarin da ke da sabar tsakiya bane ke buƙatar samun damar bayanan wuri na sirri, an ƙirƙiri tsarin tsare sirri da yawa waɗanda ke amfani da sabar tsakiya don sadarwa kawai (duba sashe na ƙasa).
