Maimakon amfani da aikace-aikacen da aka tsara don wannan dalili, tsarin ya haɗu da tattara bayanan sa ido daga tushe daban-daban, gami da bin diddigin na'urar hannu da bayanan ma'amala na katin, da isar da saƙonnin rubutu ga waɗannan mutanen da ke da cutar.
Baya ga amfani da wannan bayanan, gwamnati ta ba da damar samun bayanan wurin ga kowa, saboda canje-canje masu yawa a cikin dokokin sirrin bayanai da aka yi a wannan ƙasar sakamakon barkewar cutar MERS.
