Koyaya, PPP-PT haɗin gwiwa ne wanda ya ƙunshi duka hanyoyin tsakiya da na rarrabawa kuma ya ƙunshi yarjejeniya guda ɗaya, tare da ladabi masu haɗawa waɗanda ke da alaƙa da Gundumar Kula da Sirri na Kusan Tsaro na Sirri (DP-PPT / DP-3T), Lambobin Sadarwa na Wuta, (TCN, fka Lambobin Lamarin Sadarwa, CEN), Sirrin Sirri da Tsarin Sirri don Binciken Sadarwar Wayar Hannu (PACT) da sauransu.
