"An kafa shi ne bisa ga takaddar bincike mai taken ""Apps Gone Rogue: Kare Sirrin Keɓaɓɓun Mutane a cikin Cutar da ke yaduwa wanda aka saki a ranar 7 ga Maris, 2020. Wani ƙoƙari makamancin haka an kafa shi a MIT Media Lab tare da dandalin SafeTrace na kamfanin Enema MPC, wanda ke haɓaka fasahar tsare sirri".
